{"tid":1049422,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"組團去西藏","createTime":"2019-03-06T09:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T17:53:07.000Z","uid":26080,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2a4f0f1fab22de1c22cd6aa6544c4c17e13088fd","tid":1049422,"uid":26080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T09:07:33.000Z","msg":"時間：24/07晚機去, 04/08黃昏返到香港<br />\n景區：林芝、巴松錯、魯朗、拉薩、羊湖（露營）、納木錯<br />\n價錢：<br />\n6500人仔包早餐同車(私人包車團)<br />\n食同玩預多2000至3000人仔<br />\n機票預HK$7000以內<br />\n<br />\n影風景、銀河星空為主。成個行程係自己plan ，唔join local tour。<br />\n<br />\n呢個時間去會暖啲，一入黑就可以開始影銀河，同時係旺季，所以機票貴啲。秋/春季去會平啲，銀河唔夠靚同時間好唔方便。<br />\n<br />\n目前差一個人，4人團，有興趣tg我 @jy1122"},{"pid":"157fe83b41ebad8719b8f3deacfe9a480d347043","tid":1049422,"uid":26080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:51:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03676a47f71aea10bf8a0b414091d188df29ad54","tid":1049422,"uid":176924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:47:04.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n好似好吸引<br />\n睇下請唔請到假先"},{"pid":"aa74d3a72070646b2a9591af3775e2d9b81760d5","tid":1049422,"uid":26080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03676a47f71aea10bf8a0b414091d188df29ad54","tid":1049422,"uid":176924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:47:04.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n好似好吸引<br />\n睇下請唔請到假先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T02:02:49.000Z","msg":"Ok 既話盡快tg 我"},{"pid":"7107fa18374c44f54834f1fd205b1679fac4af6c","tid":1049422,"uid":26080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:14:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99433caf59e810237ab47c25a63d25162ecc1f19","tid":1049422,"uid":84212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T07:12:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee3c341427322a859bd4c8975d8323991df0a9cd","tid":1049422,"uid":26080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quot